text: The National Congress () is the legislative branch of the government of Honduras. The Honduran Congress is a unicameral legislature. Its members are 128 deputies, who are elected to serve four-year terms. Congress meets in a purpose-built legislative palace (Palacio Legislativo) in the centre of Tegucigalpa. ==Other websites== * Category:Politics of Honduras Category:Unicameral legislatures
